msgid "It's already unlocked."
msgstr "已經被解鎖了。"

msgid "The box contains various empty notebooks, textbooks and... chalk."
msgstr "箱子裡有著各種筆記本、課本和...粉筆。"

msgid "Take chalk?"
msgstr "拿走粉筆？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "There's nothing else of interest."
msgstr "沒什麼特別的東西了"

msgid "There's some dusty documents that catch your eye."
msgstr "一本布滿灰塵的文件引起了妳的注意。"

msgid "Read them?"
msgstr "讀它嗎？"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "It's a... lawsuit?"
msgstr "這是...一場訴訟？"

msgid "What's that doing in a place like this?"
msgstr "怎麼會出現在這種地方？"

msgid "I heard about that from my dad."
msgstr "我聽我爸說過。"

msgid "Supposedly someone sued the school because of their daughter's disappearance."
msgstr "據說有人因為他的女兒失蹤而告過學校。"

msgid "Oh, the 2nd year girl?"
msgstr "喔，一個二年級女生？"

msgid "I heard something happened, but I didn't know the school was involved."
msgstr "我聽說出了事情，但是不知道跟學校有關。"

msgid "I don't know either."
msgstr "我也不知道。"

msgid "But she was last seen at school, so her family was convinced that something happened here and it was covered up."
msgstr "但是她最後出現在學校，所以她的家人認為出了什麼意外而被隱瞞。"

msgid "There's definitely an odd history of disappearances in this town."
msgstr "這肯定是這個小鎮奇怪的歷史之一。"

msgid "When I graduate, I'm out of here."
msgstr "我畢業之後，一定會離開這裡。"

msgid "The hairpin doesn't fit into this lock."
msgstr "髮夾沒辦法插進鎖中。"

msgid "The key fits!"
msgstr "鑰匙吻合！"

msgid "The boxes are already open."
msgstr "箱子已經被打開了。"

msgid "Boxes filled with rags and other cleaning supplies."
msgstr "裝滿了抹布和其他清潔用品的箱子。"

msgid "A sealed box."
msgstr "被封起來的箱子。"

msgid "Some boxes filled with random objects."
msgstr "裝滿了各種物品的箱子。"

msgid "This is the lost and found box!"
msgstr "這是失物箱！"

msgid "Really?"
msgstr "真的嗎？"

msgid "Look, I found my old shoe."
msgstr "妳看，我找到我的舊鞋子。"

msgid "A shoe...?"
msgstr "一隻鞋子...？"

msgid "I lost it years ago."
msgstr "我一年前弄丟它的。"

msgid "How do you lose one shoe?"
msgstr "妳是怎麼弄丟一隻鞋子的？"

msgid "It just disappeared."
msgstr "它就不見了。"

msgid "Oh! My lighter!"
msgstr "喔！我的打火機！"

msgid "Don't you already have a lighter?"
msgstr "妳不是已經有打火機了嗎？"

msgid "This is my old one."
msgstr "這是舊的。"

msgid "You lost a lighter in the school?"
msgstr "妳在學校弄丟了打火機？"

msgid "No, they confiscated it."
msgstr "不是，它是被沒收的。"

msgid "Figures. Lighters can be dangerous."
msgstr "也是。打火機很危險。"

msgid "Only in the wrong hands."
msgstr "只有在壞人手上的時候。"

msgid "And yours aren't?"
msgstr "而妳不是？"

msgid "You shouldn't bring lighters to school..."
msgstr "妳不應該把打火機帶來學校..."

msgid "Some used brooms."
msgstr "一些已經用過的掃帚。"

msgid "A calendar and information sheet for the cleaning staff."
msgstr "一本日曆和清潔人員的資料表。"

msgid "A cleaning cart."
msgstr "清潔推車。"

msgid "It could use some cleaning."
msgstr "這推車應該清潔一下。"

msgid "A dusty lamp. The light bulb is missing."
msgstr "布滿灰塵的立燈。燈泡不見了。"

msgid "Well that's ominous."
msgstr "還真是不祥之兆。"

msgid "A little darkness won't hurt anybody."
msgstr "一點點黑暗傷不了人。"

msgid "...Probably."
msgstr "...大概吧。"

msgid "It doesn't work."
msgstr "沒有用。"

msgid "A large locker that could probably fit a person."
msgstr "可能可以裝一個人的大儲物櫃。"

msgid "It's locked."
msgstr "被鎖住了。"

msgid "Lots of cleaning supplies. It smells weird."
msgstr "很多清潔用品。聞起來怪怪的。"

msgid "Lots of school supplies."
msgstr "很多學校用品。"

msgid "Books and paints line the shelves."
msgstr "書本和顏料排滿了架子。"

msgid "There's a small key on one of the shelves."
msgstr "其中一個架子上有一把小鑰匙。"

msgid "Take it?"
msgstr "拿走嗎？"

msgid "A trash can, even in a place like this."
msgstr "垃圾桶，在這種地方也有。"

msgid "Why would there be a trash can in a supply closet?"
msgstr "為什麼置物間裡會有垃圾桶？"

msgid "Maybe it's a spare?"
msgstr "也許是備用的？"

msgid "It's... so dark."
msgstr "這裡...好暗。"

msgid "Come on Ponytail, don't chicken out on me now."
msgstr "別想著落跑，馬尾女。"

msgid "Don't call me that."
msgstr "不要那樣叫我。"

msgid "You have a ponytail, don't you?"
msgstr "妳有馬尾，沒錯吧？"

msgid "I have a name too."
msgstr "我也有名字。"
